title: Dare to Compare!  Take the Test!
posting_body: ['Location, Location, Location', 'Like many Walnut Creek properties, Park Place Apartments claims to be within walking distance to Broadway Plaza in Walnut Creek.', ' Put on your walking shoes, stop by the Park Place Office and ask our staff to provide you with a parking space while you go shopping or dining.', ' Take a walk.', ' Then go over to one of those other places and try the same thing.', ' See who’s truly within walking distance.', 'Where to Park?', 'Like many other downtown communities, Park Place Apartments provides each resident with one unassigned parking space.', ' Stop by the office and ask them to show you where second and/or guest cars may park?', ' Then head on over to one of those other places and ask the same thing.', ' See who’s got downtown’s best parking.', 'Park Place Apartments', 'One Bedrooms starting at', '$2245 per month']
